{{Infobox language |name=Manga |nativename= |states=China |ethnicity=[[Yi people|Yi]] |speakers=? |date= |ref= |familycolor=Sino-Tibetan |fam2=[[Lolo-Burmese languages|Lolo-Burmese]] |fam3=[[Mondzish languages|Mondzish]] |script= |iso3=none |glotto=none }}
'''Manga''' ([[Exonym and endonym|autonym]]: ''{{IPA|ma˧ŋa˧}}'') is a [[Lolo-Burmese languages|Lolo-Burmese language]] spoken by the [[Yi people]] of China. It is spoken in Gedang Village 格当村, Xinhua Township 新华乡, [[Funing County, Yunnan]] (Lama 2012).
