'''Peruvian Brazilians''' ([[Spanish language|Spanish]]: ''Peruano-brasileño'', [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]]: ''Peruano-brasileiro'') refers to [[Demographics of Brazil|Brazilian]] people of full, partial, or predominantly [[Peruvian]] ancestry.<ref>[http://www.migrationinformation.org/Profiles/display.cfm?ID=311 Peruvians in Brazil]</ref>

